(Wow! I never realized how many raptor fans there are in this club! Oh, just 
a neat lil fact: There was a new species of raptor recently discovered back 
in 1996. I can't recall where, but it dwarfs the Utahraptor! It's called a 
Megaraptor. It's pretty kewl.)

Hysteria/(Tavatron pending)

Hysteria banged her head against the bottom of the console she happened to 
be under as the red alert blared throught the ship:

"SLAG!!"

At this rate she'd never get this slaggin' console fixed! Hysteria 
immedeatly jumped to her feet and replied to IR the moment she recieved her 
comm:

"I"ll meet you there!"

Hysteria skidded down several halls before emerging in the command room. She 
ran over to the nearest console and began pulling up blueprints of the Ark. 
It would take a few minutes in order to establish a satellite link with the 
Ark in order to view recent damage, but it was doable.
